- What are you talking about?

582
00:59:48,800 --> 00:59:51,700
It's best we split up now.

583
00:59:54,400 --> 00:59:57,400
Do me a favour before you go, Albert.

584
00:59:57,600 --> 01:00:00,700
- Get rid of the dead.
- You mean that...

585
01:00:03,300 --> 01:00:05,400
I can go?

586
01:00:05,500 --> 01:00:07,700
Yeah.

587
01:00:07,800 --> 01:00:09,800
Yeah, you head south.

588
01:00:11,100 --> 01:00:14,200
And we'll all meet up in Juárez.

589
01:00:14,400 --> 01:00:16,800
What the hell's goin' on here, Mike?

590
01:00:16,900 --> 01:00:19,900
I'm killing two birds with one stone.

591
01:00:21,200 --> 01:00:24,500
