592
01:00:24,600 --> 01:00:27,200
Then they're gonna have to help us.

593
01:00:27,300 --> 01:00:30,600
- How?
- You're gonna have to drop by the bank.

594
01:00:30,800 --> 01:00:34,400
- Ten thousand would be just fine.
