595
01:00:34,500 --> 01:00:38,300
- You gonna start lying to me again?
- Someone's gonna have to go with him.

596
01:00:38,400 --> 01:00:42,300
- He's gonna go straight to the police!
- What did I tell you?

597
01:00:42,400 --> 01:00:45,900
Stop thinkin'. He's goin' all by himself.

598
01:00:47,200 --> 01:00:49,300
He's mad, but he's scared.

599
01:00:55,200 --> 01:00:57,100
Come on.

600
01:00:58,600 --> 01:01:00,800
I'll see you guys in Mexico.

601
01:01:04,500 --> 01:01:08,500
Mexico. Definitely Mexico.

602
01:01:10,400 --> 01:01:13,400
