of accused killer Michael Bosworth.

629
01:06:41,400 --> 01:06:43,400
Breyers was not available for comment.

630
01:06:43,500 --> 01:06:47,200
We'll keep you posted
with further information as it b...

631
01:06:47,300 --> 01:06:49,600
- She's in control.
