632
01:06:49,800 --> 01:06:52,300
She will.

633
01:06:52,500 --> 01:06:54,700
She will?

634
01:07:00,200 --> 01:07:03,200
What do you find so amusing?

635
01:07:03,300 --> 01:07:05,000
You.

636
01:07:19,200 --> 01:07:21,100
Wally.

637
01:07:25,700 --> 01:07:29,900
Looks like you won
the Vietnam war all by yourself.

638
01:07:45,700 --> 01:07:47,800
That's a good boy.

639
01:07:48,000 --> 01:07:50,000
I knew you wouldn't take any chances.

640
01:07:50,100 --> 01:07:52,100
- What have you got?
- I'm not sure.

641
01:07:52,200 --> 01:07:54,600
A body's been found
in the south of the county.

642
01:07:54,700 --> 01:07:58,300
A real-estate agent named Ed Tallent,
shot at point-blank range.

643
01:07:58,500 --> 01:08:01,100
- It may mean nothing.
- Where was he found?

644
01:08:01,200 --> 01:08:05,100
In a riverbed. His car is on the scene,
about five hours from here.

645
01:08:05,200 --> 01:08:11,500
Probably does mean somethin'. Get me
the addresses of all his residential listings.

646
01:08:11,600 --> 01:08:15,400
It's my opinion Bosworth believes
he can escape from anywhere.

647
01:08:15,600 --> 01:08:18,200
I'd like to start settin' up
roadblocks in the area.

648
01:08:18,300 --> 01:08:23,300
Request denied. Bosworth's in a house,
and there sure as hell are hostages.

649
01:08:23,400 --> 01:08:26,000
That's the way he plays.

650
01:08:26,100 --> 01:08:30,500
Your orders are to wait for me
to give you more orders.

651
01:08:30,600 --> 01:08:32,500
Thank you, ma'am.

652
01:08:34,800 --> 01:08:36,700
Maddox!

653
01:08:36,800 --> 01:08:40,500
If you learn anything, don't drift away!

654
01:08:41,600 --> 01:08:44,000
I'm just a cheap float in a stormy sea.

655
01:08:46,600 --> 01:08:49,300
Yeah, it was beautiful. It was great.

656
01:08:52,400 --> 01:08:54,400
I'll call you later.

657
01:08:55,800 --> 01:08:57,700
Hey.

658
01:09:04,000 --> 01:09:06,300
Which way are you guys goin'?

659
01:09:07,500 --> 01:09:09,600
Sorry.

660
01:09:11,500 --> 01:09:14,100
What college do you go to?

661
01:09:17,200 --> 01:09:19,500
- Fuck off.
- Aw, come on.

662
01:09:19,700 --> 01:09:22,900
I just need a lift a little ways. That's all.

663
01:09:23,100 --> 01:09:24,900
- Go away, please!
- Come on.

664
01:09:25,000 --> 01:09:27,700
Lisa, call the police now! Run! Run!

665
01:09:28,100 --> 01:09:29,700
Get away from me!

666
01:10:00,600 --> 01:10:03,700
We got a report of a man
