667
01:10:03,800 --> 01:10:06,600
at the gas station on Waxman Road.

668
01:10:12,100 --> 01:10:13,300
We're there.

669
01:11:53,400 --> 01:11:55,500
You, in the water!

670
01:11:55,700 --> 01:11:58,400
Drop your weapon!

671
01:12:14,400 --> 01:12:17,300
Hey! You, in the water!

672
01:12:25,600 --> 01:12:28,500
Drop your weapon!

673
01:12:29,800 --> 01:12:34,600
I'm not gonna tell you again!
Put the gun down!

674
01:12:57,400 --> 01:13:01,000
Put the gun down!

675
01:13:17,600 --> 01:13:20,900
