is registered to a Nora Cornell,

676
01:13:21,000 --> 01:13:23,000
on Whitney Drive, which is right here.

677
01:13:23,200 --> 01:13:26,500
Give me those residential listings.

678
01:13:26,600 --> 01:13:30,700
On that call the primary placed from
the phone booth - it went to a residence.

679
01:13:30,800 --> 01:13:34,500
Timothy and Nora Cornell,
1448 Whitney Drive.

680
01:13:37,900 --> 01:13:39,900
You answer now.

681
01:13:42,500 --> 01:13:45,500
Start talking.

682
01:13:45,600 --> 01:13:47,800
