- Is Michael there?

683
01:13:47,900 --> 01:13:49,700
Yes, he is.

684
01:13:51,400 --> 01:13:55,900
If this is a trick,
you can kiss your family goodbye.

685
01:13:57,200 --> 01:13:59,500
- Yes?
- Michael?

686
01:13:59,700 --> 01:14:01,600
Nancy?

687
01:14:01,800 --> 01:14:05,900
- Nancy! Where are you?
- I'm close.

688
01:14:06,000 --> 01:14:09,000
- Did they believe you?
- Of course they believed me.

689
01:14:09,200 --> 01:14:12,900
Baby, you're brilliant. Oh, you're brilliant!

690
01:14:13,000 --> 01:14:16,200
Oh, God, I miss you.

691
01:14:16,400 --> 01:14:20,700
We're at 1448 Whitney.
How long will it take?

692
01:14:20,900 --> 01:14:26,700
- I can get there in less than an hour.
- You just be careful. You stay calm.

693
01:14:26,900 --> 01:14:29,400
- Just think about us together.
- I will.

694
01:14:29,500 --> 01:14:32,000
- I love you.
- I love you too.

695
01:14:37,700 --> 01:14:40,200
She's on her way.

696
01:14:40,400 --> 01:14:44,100
She's on her way. It's almost over, Timmy.

697
01:14:44,300 --> 01:14:46,600
I'll be out of here in less than an hour.

698
01:14:46,800 --> 01:14:48,700
What about us?

699
01:14:51,600 --> 01:14:55,300
Timmy, have I ever
broken any promises to you?

700
01:14:56,900 --> 01:14:58,800
Let's go!

701
01:15:02,000 --> 01:15:06,500
- Where is she?
- She's back at the command post.

702
01:15:06,600 --> 01:15:10,900
OK, let's have it. But make it fast.

703
01:15:11,100 --> 01:15:15,800
