and anything happens tonight,

706
01:15:23,100 --> 01:15:25,200
they'll have our ugly asses in court.

707
01:15:25,400 --> 01:15:28,700
No, only one ass is involved.

708
01:15:28,800 --> 01:15:30,600
Mine.

709
01:15:30,800 --> 01:15:32,800
And what's ugly about it?

710
